title: Game launcher broke!!!
body: Yesterday i  had some problems with the client like : freezing,lagging,crashing. And today i start the client and i want to play a match,i press find match and the game freeze and after that the client(launcher)  does not open anymore... (Some help,any ideeas? No! i will not re install the game!) :)

replies.body: There's been some issues on EUNE, but our network team has been hands on deck to fix this up.  Is everything okay now?
Same here, reinstall didn't help. Any ideas?
